18 qualified authority shall publish notice of the resolution and the
19 ordinances, rules, and regulations included in the resolution or a
20 summary of the ordinances, rules, and regulations on a website
21 maintained by the qualified authority and in a newspaper of general
22 circulation within the geographic boundaries of the qualified
23 authority and any municipality outside of the geographic boundaries
24 of the qualified authority to which the qualified authority
25 provides service by contract under section 10. An ordinance, rule,
26 or regulation adopted by the governing body of a qualified
27 authority is effective 30 days after the date of publication of the
28 notice of the resolution adopting the ordinance, rule, or
29 regulation. If a summary of ordinances, rules, and regulations is
